art-of-the-heist.name: Art of the Heist
art-of-the-heist.description: Art of the Heist takes you on a night-time raid through Townsville Fine Art Gallery in the company of the greatest Art-Thief of all time, Vincenzo!

down-the-pub-desktop.name: Down the Pub
down-the-pub-desktop.description:
Down the Pub slot is the best to visit on Friday night. 5x3, 15 fixed lines slot features Wild symbol, Scatter symbols which trigger Free Spins. The last ones can be stopped only by the very last pint of beer! But keep you mind sober, as the Bonus Game will puzzle you – you’ll get to play a slot
inside a slot!

spellcraft-pc.name: Spellcraft
spellcraft-pc.description: Three witches will put a spell on you, but it’s a good one! 5x3 video slot with 27 fixed lines is a real magic to enjoy!

christmas-eve-pc.name: Christmas Eve
christmas-eve-pc.description: Are you in a holiday mood? Because we are! Playson presents the coziest and well-paying winter holiday season game – ‘Christmas Eve’. Visit Lapland this winter, but instead of spending – make money! You were nice the whole year long, so Father Christmas will bring you Frosty Wilds, which will stick on the reels and grant a re-spin!

dancing-dragon-spring-festival-pc.name: Dancing Dragon Spring Festival
dancing-dragon-spring-festival-pc.description: What is your Chinese horoscope symbol? A rabbit or a cat? Or maybe monkey? Well, ours is Dragon! Feel all the goodness to come when visiting new Playson’s Dancing Dragon Spring Festival!

7-mirrors.name: 7 Mirrors
7-mirrors.description: The reflections on these mirrors come with more than one surprise – and they are not just an optical illusion. 7 Mirrors Video Slot game has five spinning reels with 9 fixed win lines. The Golden Star is a Scatter symbol and triggers a Bonus Game.

black-mummy.name: Black Mummy
black-mummy.description: Woken up from its ancient grave, The Black Mummy becomes a Wild symbol which, when substituting for the J, Q, K and A symbols, awards up to 5x multipliers.

blackbeards-quest.name: Blackbeard's Quest
blackbeards-quest.description: Meet the frightening pirate Blackbeard on his new quest to a treasure island! When Blackbeard goes Wild, it enables extra winning combinations on the 9 win lines, and when 3 Treasure Chests appear on the 1st, 3rd, and 5th reel, they trigger retriggerable Free Spins. During Free Spins, these Chests become Wild and substitute for all symbols except Blackbeard.

book-of-spells.name: Book of Spells
book-of-spells.description: In the land of witchcraft, potions, and magic, the Book of Spells will turn its own pages to help players win. Book of Spells is a Wild Symbol and substitutes for all other symbols, spinning around 5 reels to increase the number of winning combinations formed on the 9 win lines of the game. When 3 or more Books of Spells are scattered on the reels, they trigger 10 retriggerable Free Spins with special expanding symbol for bigger wins.

cleopatras-secret.name: Cleopatra's Secret
cleopatras-secret.description: The irresistible charm of a dazzling Egyptian queen Cleopatra makes this game one of the most attractive video slots of our days. Cleopatra’s Secret has 5 spinning reels with 25 win lines and it is attractive not only for its stylish graphics, but also for its tempting features such as the Wild Sphinx symbol that trebles your wins and the Mummy that will award you with retriggerable Free Spins

don-juans-peppers.name: Don Juan's Peppers
don-juans-peppers.description: Don Juan’s Peppers Ranch produces the most wanted twirls in Southern Mexico. The Sun will shine as a Wild symbol to help you get the hottest combinations. 3 or more Red Chili Peppers trigger up to 25 Free Spins, and every time one lands during the feature, it awards you an extra Free Spin and transforms into Sticky Scatter Wild symbol for the remainder of Free Spins, making your win even spicier.

double-flash.name: Double Flash
double-flash.description: Your chance to win is doubled in Double Flash! Every fruit appears twice on each position in this 27-win line slot game. Coloured double symbols pay DOUBLE the winline win!

dragon-egg.name: Dragon Egg
dragon-egg.description: The eggs laid by these dragons are the key to winning in this game. Its 9 win lines are the perfect environment for the Wild Winged Dragon to spread its wings and double your wins when substituting for other symbols. The Scatter Eggs trigger a Bonus Feature in which collecting three eggs from the same dragon awards you from 10 to 30 Free Spins with 3x to 5x multiplier.

feng-fu.name: Feng Fu
feng-fu.description: Fortune and luck abide in Feng Fu. The Ying-Yang symbol will give away free spins and multipliers in its role as a Wild Scatter. During these free spins the Dragon acts as a special expanding Wild and will double any winnings on active paylines.

fire-and-hot.name: Fire and Hot
fire-and-hot.description: Fortune and luck abide in Feng Fu. The Ying-Yang symbol will give away free spins and multipliers in its role as a Wild Scatter. During these free spins the Dragon acts as a special expanding Wild and will double any winnings on active paylines.

fruit.name: Fruit
fruit.description: We have transformed a classic fruit machine into a fresh and juicy fruit cocktail. This classy game has 5 spinning reels with 15 win lines and a revamped set of splendid fruit, everything from cherries to kiwis. There are Free Spins and the Fruit plate symbol is Wild.

golf-championship.name: Golf Championship
golf-championship.description: Strong winds and unpleasant weather are no longer an impediment to win a Golf Championship. With 5 spinning reels and 9 win lines, this game includes a Scatter and the Golf Cup is Wild.

hammer-of-thor.name: Hammer of Thor
hammer-of-thor.description: Release the power of the ancient gods of Valhalla, increase your winnings with the anger of God Thor, whose lightning will certainly secure a prize. Fighting dragons and the skulls of your enemies will award you even more treasures. The golden win line doubles your win in this 9-win line game.

hot-blizzard.name: Hot Blizzard
hot-blizzard.description: The ice cold ‚7‘ symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Lucky Star Scatter. That won’t be an issue, since all wins during free spins will be multiplied by 3! You can win from 10 to 30 free spins.

jingle-bells-tomhorn.name: Jingle Bells
jingle-bells-tomhorn.description: It does not have to be Christmas for these bells to jingle. This entertaining video slot game has 27 fixed win lines laid across three reels for fun lovers to play and win. The game is enhanced with a Bonus Feature that awards either a bonus win or Free Spins. The Jester symbol is a wild card.

luna-park.name: Luna Park
luna-park.description: Never ending amusement starts at the Luna Park. The game has 5 spinning reels with 9 win lines for greater chances of winning. There is a SCATTER symbol and the Russian Wheel symbol is Wild

middle-earth.name: Middle Earth
middle-earth.description: Never ending amusement starts at the Luna Park. The game has 5 spinning reels with 9 win lines for greater chances of winning. There is a SCATTER symbol and the Russian Wheel symbol is Wild

royal-double.name: Royal Double
royal-double.description: Royal Double is not just a regular 27-win line game, it has the incredible symbols 'x2' that double your win per line. Along with the Joker and the random Mystery Prize feature, this slot game is one that you cannot miss.

savannah-king.name: Savannah King
savannah-king.description: The King of the jungle is worthy of the WILD symbol, but the green diamonds act as DOUBLE WILD, where they will double the winnings on any active winlines during freespins. Baobab trees will award free spins when at least 3 are obtained.

sky-barons.name: Sky Barons
sky-barons.description: Join the Red Baron and the Jasta 11 in this fantastic mission! The Wild Nurse symbol can disguise itself as any other symbol, except the Scatter Pilot and the Medal, and appears only after the Pilot has triggered Free Spins. Victories in combat are rewarded with the Medal; this symbol increases the Free Spins multiplier by ONE and goes as high as 13x.

thrones-of-persia.name: Thrones of Persia
thrones-of-persia.description: The treasures of ancient Persia, full of Wild and Extra Wild symbols automatically doubling wins during free spins, await the brave players. 3 Scatters launch a Zikkurat bonus game where by revealing symbols you might get lucky and obtain more free spins with a higher multiplier.

wheel-of-luck.name: Wheel of Luck
wheel-of-luck.description: Spin the Wheel of Luck and prepare for high winnings and bonuses. Wheel of Luck has 5 spinning reels with 25 win lines. The game includes a special extra Bonus feature. The Wheel of Luck symbol is Wild and can substitute for other symbols, except Scatter, to complete more winning combinations.

wild-pearl.name: Wild Pearl
wild-pearl.description: Swim with the Dolphins into the deep sea and collect a treasure of precious pearls. Wild Pearl has 9 winning lines on which the Wild Dolphin doubles every win in which it substitutes and the Scatter Pearls release retriggerable bundles of 15 Free Spins. A 3x multiplier is applied before retrigger

wild-sierra.name: Wild Sierra
wild-sierra.description: Mighty bears, gracious wolfs along with other animals wander and hunt in the Wild Sierra. Wild Sierra symbol acts as a joker and substitutes for all symbols except the Tree of Life, which is a Scatter symbol. 3 or more Trees of Life grouped on the reels trigger 5 retriggerable Free Spins with total bet multiplied by 2.

wonders-of-the-ancient-world.name: Wonders of the Ancient World
wonders-of-the-ancient-world.description: Admire the Wonders of the Ancient World on five spinning reels with 15 win lines. Its Bonus Game and Free Spins will give players special excitement and big winning opportunities. The Lighthouse symbol is Wild.

viking-gods-thor-and-loki-pc.name: Viking Gods: Thor and Loki
viking-gods-thor-and-loki-pc.description: Feel the power of Old Norse Gods in the new 3x5 video slot ‘Viking Gods: Thor and Loki’ by Playson.

kingdom-of-the-sun--golden-age-pc.name: Kingdom of the Sun : Golden Age
kingdom-of-the-sun--golden-age-pc.shortName: Kingdom of the Sun : Golden Age

sevens--fruits-pc.name: Sevens & Fruits
sevens--fruits-pc.description:
Sevens&Fruits is a classic fruit slot for those who want a simple, good play with big winnings. Fresh juicy fruits with vivid fire animations and a classic sound is a gift for those gamblers who admire old slots. Everything is straightforward here: there are no special bonus or free spins. 
But there are fiery red Seven symbols which compose most fruitful combinations; Star symbols which are Scatters and pay independently of 5 bet lines. 
Simple, elegant, addictive - that's all you have to remember about the Sevens&Fruits slot!

spinomenal_divine-forest.name: Divine Forest
spinomenal_divine-forest.description: Explore the forest as you complete missions to unlock features. We would like to invite you to take a short break from the everyday rush and stress and welcome you to the fairytale we created especially for you. Divine forest has amazing new features and absolutely magical setting!

joker-expand-40-lines-pc.name: Joker Expand: 40 lines
joker-expand-40-lines-pc.description:
“Joker Expand: 40 lines” is a sequel to royal harlequin games from Playson. In this 4x5
video slot, Wild symbol is drawn as Joker, which expands to full-figure with a chance of winnings.
This video slot also features 2 types of Scatters: Gold Scatter, and Diamond Scatter. Scatter
wins pay regardless of pay lines. Red sevens are to bring the highest payout. And the rest of the
symbols will bring some fruitful combinations for sure.

spinomenal_parrots-rock.name: Parrots Rock
spinomenal_parrots-rock.description: Get ready to rock out! Parrots Rock is a guaranteed joyful experience, packed with hard rocking bets, and head banging wins! Get your groove on now and try the amazing Parrots Rock!

playson_wild-warriors.name: Wild Warriors
playson_wild-warriors.description: Legendary era of warrior ladies is back with the “Wild Warriors” release from Playson. This 3x5 video slot with 30 lines features female fighters as the high paying symbols.

fruitsandclovers-20-lines-pc.name: Fruits&Clovers: 20 lines
fruitsandclovers-20-lines-pc.description: Timeless Fruits Slots collection by Playson has a new vibrant addition -“Fruits&Clovers: 20 lines”.A classic fruits slotset on a 3x5 gridwith memorable fruit symbols is topped with lucky clovers, which act as Wild symbols and land in stacks on the reels. Star symbol is a Scatter and pays regardless of pay lines. And the eye-catching red sevens are to bring impressive payouts.

sevensandfruits-20-lines-pc.name: Sevens&Fruits: 20 lines
sevensandfruits-20-lines-pc.description: ‘Sevens&Fruits: 20 lines’ is a new addition to ‘Timeless Fruit Slots’ collection by Playson and a sequel to the very first release in the series. It is a classic fruit slot for those who want a simple, good play with big winnings. Fiery red Seven symbols compose most fruitful combinations and Star symbols which are Scatters, pay independently of bet lines.

imperial-fruits-5-lines.name: Imperial Fruits: 5 lines
imperial-fruits-5-lines.description: “Imperial Fruits: 5lines”brings in the royal touch to the “Timeless Fruit Slots”collection by introducing the new feature symbol Wild Crown. In this 3x5 video slot,where crown acts as Wild symbol, which expands to increase the chance of composing a winning combination.This video slot features 2 types of Scatters: Gold Scatter, and Diamond Scatter. Scatter wins pay regardless of pay lines. Red sevens are to bring the highest payout. And the rest of the symbols will bring some fruitful combinations for sure.
